Despite her health issues, Parton hasn’t lost her sense of humor –
joking that she told her doctors,
“It must be time for my 100,000-mile checkup,
although it’s not the usual trip to see my plastic surgeon!”
The singer also noted that she doesn’t have any plans to retire,
telling fans: “While I’ll still be able to work on all of
my projects from here in Nashville,
I just need a little time to get show ready, as they say.
And don’t worry about me quittin’
the business because God hasn’t said anything about stopping yet.”
